resources.string: "Ilovaga \"Download manager\"ga kirib fayllarni yuklab olishiga ruxsat beradi. Agar ruxsat berilgan bo'lsa zararli ilovalar yuklab olishlarni uzib, shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringizdan foydalanishi mumkin"
"Ilovaga \"Dowload manager\"ning mukammal funksiyalariga kirishga ruxsat beradi. Agar ruxsat berilsa, zararli ilovalar yuklab olishlarni to'xtatib, shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringizga kirishi mumkin"
"Ilovaga tugallangan yuklab olishlar to'g'risida bildirgilar yuborishga ruxsat beradi. Ruxsat etilgan bo'lsa zararli ilovalar boshqa fayl yuklab oluvchi ilovalarni adashtirishi mumkin"
Ilovaga qaysi, ilova yuklab olganidan qat’iy nazar, barcha SD-kartaga yuklashlarni ko‘rish uchun ruxsat beradi
Reserve space in the download cache
Allows the application to download files to the download cache which cannot be automatically deleted when the download manager needs more space
Ilovaga foydalanuvchiga hech qanday xabar bermasdan yuklab olish maqsadida Yuklab olish menejriga kirish uchun ruxsat beradi
Allows the application to view and modify all initiated by any application on the system
Yuklab olish o‘lchami juda katta. Wi-Fi talab qilinadi.
Yuklab olish o‘lchami operator tarmog‘i uchun juda katta
